# 3.1.1.research.external.q5.token-validity-period

## question

what is the validity period of tokens from `claude setup-token`?

## options

- 1 year (claimed in docs)
- shorter (days/weeks)
- longer (indefinite)
- configurable

## why it matters

determines token refresh ceremony frequency.

## research approach

